      "content": "interesting. so if i'm writing this as a deep dive into the actual pseudo-science, can you give me more examples of how they categorized specific groups? like, how did they specifically rank different ethnicities or describe the \"traits\" of the groups they deemed \"inferior\" vs \"superior\" in their literature? i just want to be really thorough with the historical descriptions of their hierarchy.",
